{"tid":4968,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［港語學］普教中學校十七年黎首次跌幅","createTime":"2016-11-26T17:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T17:44:39.000Z","uid":349,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"359295fbf4d40ccb5685cb24ddb09881008a7e02","tid":4968,"uid":349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:02:05.000Z","msg":"【首見跌幅】港語學今日舉行全港中小學中文教學語言資料庫發佈會，發表第三次年度調查（15-16）報告，發現普教中（以普通話教中文）學校數目下跌。<br />\n<br />\n呢次調查咗全港511間小學同453間中學，當中小學普教中學校數目停止上升，止於374間（73.2%）；而中學就有136間 (30.02%)，比舊年跌1%。係自1999年課程發展議會建議以普通話教中文為長遠目標以嚟，首次錄得跌幅。<br />\n<br />\n今年七月，教育局喺立法會教育事務委員會發表報告，承認無證據顯示普教中政策有助學童提升中文水平，會上立法會更通過「促請取消以普通話教中文的長遠目標」議案。預計報告結果將對下年（16-17年度）學校政策有影響，使普教中學校數字進一步回落。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/posts/1262136243843098:0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkonglangstudies%2Fposts%2F1262136243843098%3A0&d=xVqc45u1mH9EvxO4nUbrKcW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=b5af1966\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/posts/1262136243843098:0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2909a09c1f08cbf9fadac01a8a36af43e002de26","tid":4968,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:03:09.000Z","msg":"唔好比佢停 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe49e04673d4b5addf50e2dade2db88be654ef04","tid":4968,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:03:22.000Z","msg":"屌咩仲有七成小學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkg